with the Fengxiang Palace,

144
00:05:22,590 --> 00:05:23,990
His Majesty would never spare
the Hua Family.

145
00:05:25,390 --> 00:05:26,470
I have already failed Hua Zhi.

146
00:05:27,150 --> 00:05:27,870
