271
00:09:14,870 --> 00:09:15,990
When we got raided,

272
00:09:16,150 --> 00:09:17,310
she didn't only stash money

273
00:09:18,110 --> 00:09:19,150
but also an abacus!

274
00:09:19,870 --> 00:09:21,870
